           move      rf-sff-sgl-vlt       to   w-exe-sgl-vlt          .
           move      rf-sff-dec-vlt       to   w-exe-dec-vlt          .
           move      rf-sff-tdc-vlt       to   w-exe-tdc-vlt          .
           move      rf-sff-cdc-ftf       to   w-exe-cdc-vlt          .
           perform   exe-gen-vlt-000      thru exe-gen-vlt-999        .
